13 FRAMEWORK
14 §3301. Legislative findings and purpose
15 The legislature hereby finds and declares all of the following:
16 (1) Biomedical innovation and clinical research are important drivers of
17 patient access to investigational therapies, improvements in public health, private
18 investment, and economic growth.
